com.mapspeople.models

Interface Location

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Feature
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MPLocation, PositionIndicator

    public interface Location
extends Feature
    Location model. Implement this interface to create and use your own locations. Use in conjunction with a provider interface implementation/extension.
